info.author: Andy Rhind
info.description: This package wraps and extends the QNX6 RealTime operating system features. It provides modules that expose the Time, Messaging, Interrupts and Resource Manager features of QNX6. Its intention is as a learning/prototyping/play tool. it is not intended for production.
info.name: PyQNX6
info.summary: Python/QNX6 wrapper for Timer,Message, Interrupt and Resource Managers.
